<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Creator Blog Post - WoW Central</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Content/Site.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-image: url('/images/background.jpg'); 
            background-size: cover;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            color: #fff;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
        }

        .site-name h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #ffcc00;
        }

        .navbar ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
        }

        .navbar ul li {
            margin: 0 15px;
        }

        .navbar ul li a {
            color: #ffcc00;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .navbar ul li a:hover {
            color: #ff6600;
        }

        main {
            padding: 50px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            margin: 20px auto;
            max-width: 800px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .blog-container {
            text-align: left;
        }

        .blog-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #ffcc00;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .blog-author {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #ffcc00;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .blog-content {
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .blog-image img {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .comment-section {
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .comment-section h3 {
            color: #ffcc00;
        }

        .comment-form textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border: none;
            resize: vertical;
        }

        .comment-form button {
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #ff6600;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .comment-form button:hover {
            background-color: #ffcc00;
        }

        .comment {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .comment p {
            margin: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="header-container">
            <div class="site-name">
                <h1>WoW Central</h1>
            </div>
            <nav class="navbar">
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/blogs/featured">Featured Blogs</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/blogs/myblogs">My Blogs</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>
    <main>
        <div class="blog-container">
            <h2 class="blog-title">The Secrets of Azeroth</h2>
            <p class="blog-author">by <strong>ThrallFan99</strong></p>
            <div class="blog-image">
                <img src="/images/azeroth_secrets.jpg" alt="Secrets of Azeroth">
            </div>
            <div class="blog-content">
                <p>
                    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Proin scelerisque, mauris at viverra aliquet, risus purus tempor nisl, a interdum nunc sapien in nunc. Ut condimentum, massa non pretium facilisis, augue risus sagittis sem, ac viverra nunc felis id urna.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Suspendisse potenti. Quisque nec turpis ligula. Integer eu elit magna. Nam euismod, lacus a faucibus faucibus, sapien eros posuere orci, vel bibendum libero nisi ac augue.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="comment-section">
            <h3>Comments</h3>
            <div class="comment">
                <p><strong>PlayerOne:</strong> Amazing blog! I never knew about these secrets!</p>
            </div>
            <div class="comment">
                <p><strong>Raider42:</strong> Great insights, keep up the good work!</p>
            </div>
            <form class="comment-form">
                <textarea rows="4" placeholder="Write a comment..."></textarea>
                <button type="submit">Post Comment</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
